blog/all/salesmate-email-widget-adds-delivery-and-tracking-visibility/";s:4:"time";a:2:{i:0;i:1768392000;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:13:"last-modified";a:2:{i:0;i:1768045724;i:1;a:2:{s:6:"offset";i:18000;s:6:"is_dst";b:0;}}s:4:"text";s:396:"<p>Salesmate updated the email widget inside Contacts and Deals to display delivery status, tracking info, and the channel used—reducing the need to check separate logs.</p>
<p>Where to find it: Contacts/Deals → Email Widget.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://www.salesmate.io/blog/january-2026-release-notes/">https://www.salesmate.io/blog/january-2026-release-notes/</a></p>
